description:
Are you ready for Jesus' Second Coming?

This #short clip from Pastor Ted Wilson's weekly message encourages us that the best time to prepare for Jesus' return is now. The signs of His coming are everywhere, and we must all prepare. We must all be ready to look up and witness His glory on that blessed day.

Watch the full video to hear Pastor Ted Wilson's words of encouragement, reminding us to watch and prepare for the arrival of our King.
https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=SPdj-Q8YDNo&list=PL-k2Gb-DBYo_ANrUJhHN2_4bSlMDTjuqQ&index=28
